OL,3,CInquiry into rogue surgeon to hear
OL,4,Copening statements
OL,6,FA public inquiry into disgraced
OL,7,Fneurosurgeon Sam Eljamel is to hear
OL,8,Ffrom core participants as they make
OL,9,Fopening statements.
OL,11,FMr Eljamel was head of neurosurgery at
OL,12,FDundee's Ninewells Hospital from 1995
OL,13,Funtil his suspension in December 2013,
OL,14,Fduring which time he is thought to
OL,15,Fhave harmed dozens of patients and
OL,16,Fleft some with life-changing injuries.
OL,18,FFollowing his suspension, the surgeon
OL,19,Fresigned from his post in May 2014 and
OL,20,Fremoved himself from the General
OL,21,FMedical Register in 2015.
