OL,3,CInquiry into rogue surgeon to hear
OL,4,Copening statements
OL,6,FThe Eljamel Inquiry into his
OL,7,Fprofessional practice was announced by
OL,8,Fthe Scottish Government in September
OL,9,F2023 and its terms of reference were
OL,10,Fset out by Scottish Health Secretary
OL,11,FNeil Gray earlier this year.
OL,13,FIts remit includes how concerns about
OL,14,FMr Eljamel were responded to by his
OL,15,Femployer NHS Tayside and whether the
OL,16,Fsystems in place to protect patients
OL,17,Fwere adequate.
