OL,3,CInquiry into rogue surgeon to hear
OL,4,Copening statements
OL,6,FJamie Dawson KC, senior counsel to the
OL,7,Finquiry, and Joanna Cherry KC, for the
OL,8,Fpatient group, will make opening
OL,9,Fstatements at a hearing in Edinburgh
OL,10,Fon Wednesday, as will Una Doherty KC
OL,11,Ffor NHS Tayside and Laura Thomson KC
OL,12,Ffor Scottish ministers.
OL,14,FOn Thursday, the inquiry will hear
OL,15,Fstatements on behalf of Healthcare
OL,16,FImprovement Scotland, NHS Education
OL,17,Ffor Scotland and the Royal College of
OL,18,FSurgeons (Edinburgh).
