OL,6,FThe inquiry will also hear a
OL,7,Fsubmission on behalf of the
OL,8,FIndependent Clinical Review (ICR),
OL,9,Fwhich is not a core participant.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday Mr Dawson will also
OL,12,Fprovide detail about plans for future
OL,13,Fhearings for the inquiry, as it moves
OL,14,Fcloser to the start of its evidential
OL,15,Fhearings in 2026.
