OL,3,CInquiry into rogue surgeon to hear
OL,4,Copening statements
OL,6,FSection one, the first block of
OL,7,Fhearings, will examine the background
OL,8,Fto the inquiry's terms of reference
OL,9,Fincluding the roles of key bodies,
OL,10,Findividuals, policies and practices
OL,11,Frelevant to matters being looked at by
OL,12,Fthe probe.
OL,14,FIt will look at areas including the
OL,15,Fbroad trajectory of Mr Eljamel's
OL,16,Fcareer in Scotland, the types of work
OL,17,Fhe undertook and the systems
OL,18,Fsurrounding his NHS practice.
